vaanam ( english : vaanam ) is a 1988 indian tamil film , directed by krish and produced by prabhu deva . the film stars sivaji ganesan , prabhu ganesan , anushka shetty , shakti kapoor , shakti kapoor , prabhu deva , and vadivelu . the film is a remake of the telugu film vaanam vaanam . the film was remade in telugu as vaanam &lt;unk&gt; .